quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  2,270,aur tum ( khuda ki raah mein ) jis terhan ka kharch karo ya koi Nazar manu khuda is ko jaanta hai aur zaalmon ka koi madadgaar nahi
  2,271,agar tum khairaat zahir do to woh bhi khoob hai aur agar posheeda do aur do bhi ahal haajat ko to woh khoob tar hai aur ( is terhan ka dena ) tumahray gunaaho ko bhi daur kardey ga. aur khuda ko tumahray sab kamon ki khabar hai
  2,272,"( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tum un logon ki hadaayat ke zimma daar nahi ho balkay khuda hi jis ko chahta hai hadaayat bkhshta hai. aur ( momino ) tum jo maal kharch karo ge to is ka faida tumhe ko hai aur tum jo kharch karo ge khuda ki khushnodi ke liye karo ge. aur jo maal tum kharch karo ge woh tumhe poora poora day diya jaye ga aur tumhara kuch nuqsaan nahikiya jaye ga ,"
  2,273,( aur haan tum jo kharch karo ge to ) un hajatmandon ke liye jo khuda ki raah mein ruke baithy hain aur malik mein kisi taraf jaane ki taaqat nahi rakhtay ( aur mangnay se aar rakhtay hain ) yahan taq ke nah mangnay ki wajah se nawaqif shakhs un ko ghanni khayaal karta hai aur tum qayafay se un ko saaf pehchan lau ( ke hajatmand hain aur sharam ke sabab ) logon se ( munh phore kar aur ) lapat kar nahi maang satke aur tum jo maal kharch karo ge kuch shak nahi ke khuda is ko jaanta hai
  2,274,jo log apna maal raat aur din aur posheeda aur zahir ( raah khuda mein ) kharch karte rehtay hain un ka sila perwar-digaar ke paas hai aur un ko ( qayamat ke din ) nah kisi terhan ka khauf hoga aur nah gham
